defaultThe UK Food and Drink Manufacturing Industrydefault&#xa0;
defaultThe Food and Drink Federation (FDF) rep
defaultresents the food and drink manufacturing industry, the largest manufacturing sector in the UK, employing 400,000 people.  The industry has an annual turnover of over £76bn accounting 
defaultfor 15% of the total manufacturing sector.  Exports amount to over £12bn 
defaultof which 77% goes to EU members. The industry buys two-thirds of all UK’s agricultural produce.
